overview: After a series of personal mishaps, the gang decides to place a bet on who can go the longest without having sex. In this hilarious sequel to the best selling original parody, Krammer, Gorge, Elaina and Gerry do their utmost to outlast each other in this contest of celibacy. Who will falter first? Who will be the last to succumb to their carnal desires?
title: Seinfeld 2: A XXX Parody
